  "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation\n\nCreate comprehensive Storybook stories for all 13 components covering: all variants/sizes, all states (default, hover, focus, disabled, error), all themes, composition with other components, and responsive behavior. Use CEM-driven autodocs.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/hx-library/src/components/*/hx-*.stories.ts\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Every component has stories for all visual variants\n- [ ] State stories: default, hover, focus, active, disabled, error\n- [ ] Theme stories: all available themes demonstrated\n- [ ] Composition stories: common component combinations\n- [ ] Controls for all public properties\n- [ ] CEM-driven autodocs configured\n\n**Complexity:** large",
